commit.message:
re PR target/47696 ([AVR] Compilation for atmega2560 produces incomplete interrupt vector table (USART2,3))

	PR target/47696
	* config/avr/avr-devices.c (avr_mcu_types): Fix ATmega2560 device
	description.

From-SVN: r170137
